            <svg class="w-7 h-7 group-hover:rotate-12 transition-transform duration-300" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
              <path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:stdoah">Trust without friction</h3>
          
          <div class="space-y-6 flex-grow" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:pillar-content-3">
            <div data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:tieback-part-3">
              <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest block mb-2" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:lbl-3">TieBack</span>
              <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:txt-3">A fast, mobile-first scan experience that resolves to the right view for the consumer, partner, or auditor — with controlled messaging and consistent brand tone.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pt-6 border-t border-slate-100 mt-auto" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:gap-part-3">
              <span class="text-slate-600 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest block mb-2" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:lbl-gap-3">The Gap</span>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:txt-gap-3">QR experiences often become thin landing pages that don't match real consumer needs. They lack structure, localisation, and operational control.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Pillar 4: Operational control -->
        <div class="group bg-white p-10 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 hover:border-blue-200 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-blue-500/5 transition-all duration-500 flex flex-col h-full opacity-0 translate-y-12 data-reveal-delay-300" data-reveal="fade-up" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:pillar-4">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:bg-blue-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:pillar-icon-4">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect width="7" height="9" x="3" y="3" rx="1"/>
              <rect width="7" height="5" x="14" y="3" rx="1"/>
              <rect width="7" height="9" x="14" y="12" rx="1"/>
              <rect width="7" height="5" x="3" y="16" rx="1"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:stdoag">Operational control for rollout</h3>
          
          <div class="space-y-6 flex-grow" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:pillar-content-4">
            <div data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:tieback-part-4">
              <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest block mb-2" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:lbl-4">TieBack</span>
              <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:txt-4">Governed workspaces, auditability, and rollout tools (market packs, readiness snapshots) that help teams launch safely across regions — and update content without chaos.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pt-6 border-t border-slate-100 mt-auto" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:gap-part-4">
              <span class="text-slate-600 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest block mb-2" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:lbl-gap-4">The Gap</span>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:txt-gap-4">Rollouts depend on manual processes and scattered ownership across teams. It becomes difficult to prove what changed, when, and why.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Large Visual Block -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:visual-feature">
     <div class="container mx-auto px-6" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:vf-container">
        <div class="relative h-[600px] rounded-[3rem] overflow-hidden group shadow-2xl bg-slate-900" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:vf-img-wrap">
           <img crossorigin="anonymous"
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1646154949919-e8f589c17b18?auto=format&w=1200&q=80"
            srcset="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1646154949919-e8f589c17b18?auto=format&w=320&q=80 320w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1646154949919-e8f589c17b18?auto=format&w=480&q=80 480w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1646154949919-e8f589c17b18?auto=format&w=640&q=80 640w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1646154949919-e8f589c17b18?auto=format&w=768&q=80 768w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1646154949919-e8f589c17b18?auto=format&w=1024&q=80 1024w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1646154949919-e8f589c17b18?auto=format&w=1280&q=80 1280w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1646154949919-e8f589c17b18?auto=format&w=1920&q=80 1920w"
            sizes="100vw"
            alt="Safety and verification" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:vf-img" />
           <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-slate-900/40 group-hover:bg-slate-900/30 transition-colors" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:vf-overlay"></div>
           <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-12 md:p-20 text-white max-w-2xl" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:vf-content">
              <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:vf-title">A single source of truth across markets.</h2>
              <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:vf-p">Ensure every product has accurate, up-to-date safety information no matter where it lands.</p>
           </div>
        </div>
     </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Relevant Use Cases -->
  <section class="py-32 bg-slate-50 border-y border-slate-200" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:evidence-section">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:evidence-content">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:evidence-grid-wrap">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between mb-16 gap-6" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:evidence-h-wrap">
          <div data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:ev-h-left">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:evidence-h">Relevant Use Cases</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:ev-h-p">How TieBack solves specific challenges for FMCG and food brands.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/use-cases/" class="text-blue-600 font-bold flex items-center gap-2 hover:gap-3 transition-all" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:ev-h-link">
            View All Use Cases <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" /></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:use-cases-grid">
           <!-- Use Case 1: Safety, recalls & comms -->
           <a href="/use-cases/product-safety-recalls/" class="group bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 hover:border-blue-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-blue-500/5 transition-all" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:uc-1">
             <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-blue-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:uc-icon-1">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" /></svg>
             </div>
             <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-slate-900" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:uc-h-1">Safety, recalls & comms</h4>
             <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:uc-p-1">Precise messaging right at the product level for batch recalls and time-sensitive alerts.</p>
           </a>
           
           <!-- Use Case 2: Compliance readiness -->
           <a href="/use-cases/compliance-readiness/" class="group bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 hover:border-blue-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-blue-500/5 transition-all" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:uc-2">
             <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-blue-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:uc-icon-2">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
             </div>
             <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-slate-900" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:uc-h-2">Compliance readiness</h4>
             <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:uc-p-2">Build a robust data foundation ahead of new transparency laws and industry mandates.</p>
           </a>
           
           <!-- Use Case 3: Compliance enforcement -->
           <div class="group bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 hover:border-blue-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-blue-500/5 transition-all" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:uc-3">
             <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-blue-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:uc-icon-3">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" /></svg>
             </div>
             <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-slate-900" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:uc-h-3">Compliance enforcement</h4>
             <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:uc-p-3">Audit and trace standards compliance directly to specific suppliers and production batches.</p>
           </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Final CTA -->
  <section id="request-access" class="py-32 bg-white relative overflow-hidden" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:cloe6u">
    <script>
      const observerOptions = {
        root: null,
        rootMargin: '0px',
        threshold: 0.1
      };

      const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
        entries.forEach(entry => {
          if (entry.isIntersecting) {
            const el = entry.target as HTMLElement;
            const delay = el.getAttribute('data-reveal-delay-100') ? 100 : 
                          el.getAttribute('data-reveal-delay-300') ? 300 : 0;
            
            setTimeout(() => {
              el.classList.remove('opacity-0', 'translate-y-12', 'translate-y-8', '-translate-x-12', 'translate-x-12', 'scale-105');
              el.classList.add('opacity-100', 'translate-y-0', 'translate-x-0', 'scale-100');
            }, delay);
            
            observer.unobserve(el);
          }
        });
      }, observerOptions);

      document.querySelectorAll('[data-reveal]').forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
    </script>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_bottom_left,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-blue-50/50 via-transparent to-transparent pointer-events-none" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:cta-grad"></div>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 text-center" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:8ygl36">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:8ygl37">
        <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8 tracking-tight" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:e4yr28">Ready for complete <span class="text-blue-600" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:9eb0t3">clarity?</span></h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:8k9454">
          Join the leading FMCG and food brands building their digital identity strategy on TieBack.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-6" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:8ygl38">
          <button class="w-full sm:w-auto px-12 py-5 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300 shadow-2xl shadow-blue-500/20 hover:-translate-y-1" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:y6o4u0">
            Request Early Access
          </button>
          <a href="/platform/why-tieback/" class="group text-slate-900 font-bold flex items-center gap-3 transition-colors hover:text-blue-600" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:1gb7hp">
            Why TieBack <svg class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" /></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
---
import BaseLayout from &#x27;@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro&#x27;;
import { SITE } from &#x27;@/config/site&#x27;;

const title = &quot;FMCG &amp; Food — TieBack&quot;;
const description = &quot;Sicherheitshinweise, präzise Rückrufe und marktgerechte Produkttransparenz für Marken aus den Bereichen FMCG und Lebensmittel.&quot;;
---

<BaseLayout title=<astro-expr id="3">
  description={description}
  &gt;
  <!-- 1. Industry Hero -->
  <section class="relative pt-32 pb-24 md:pt-52 md:pb-40 overflow-hidden bg-slate-950" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:cloe6q">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-40 transition-transform duration-1000 scale-105" data-reveal="zoom-out" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:hero-img-wrap">
       <img crossorigin="anonymous"
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1760463921696-04ee4607c4aa?auto=format&w=1200&q=80"
        srcset="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1760463921696-04ee4607c4aa?auto=format&w=320&q=80 320w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1760463921696-04ee4607c4aa?auto=format&w=480&q=80 480w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1760463921696-04ee4607c4aa?auto=format&w=640&q=80 640w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1760463921696-04ee4607c4aa?auto=format&w=768&q=80 768w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1760463921696-04ee4607c4aa?auto=format&w=1024&q=80 1024w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1760463921696-04ee4607c4aa?auto=format&w=1280&q=80 1280w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1760463921696-04ee4607c4aa?auto=format&w=1920&q=80 1920w"
        sizes="100vw"
        alt="Modern supermarket aisle" class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:hero-img" />
       <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-950/80 via-slate-950/40 to-slate-950" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:hero-overlay"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:6g628h">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center opacity-0 translate-y-8 transition-all duration-1000" data-reveal="fade-up" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:6g627v">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 py-1 px-3 mb-8 text-[11px] font-bold tracking-widest text-blue-400 uppercase bg-blue-500/10 backdrop-blur-md border border-blue-500/20 rounded-full" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:771h9b">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-400 animate-pulse" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:9eb0t6"></span>
          Branchenfokus
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white mb-8 leading-[1.05]" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:jg65d">
          FMCG
          &amp; <span class="text-blue-500" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:9eb0t5">Lebensmittel</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-300 mb-12 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:8k945v">
          Lebensmittel- und FMCG-Marken benötigen eine zuverlässige Möglichkeit, Produktinformationen auf dem neuesten Stand zu halten und Sicherheitshinweise direkt am Einsatzort präzise zu kommunizieren. TieBack bietet eine dynamische digitale Identitätsschicht.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-5" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:6g627u">
          <a href="#request-access" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-10 py-4 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-semibold rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 shadow-xl shadow-blue-500/20 hover:-translate-y-1" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:1gb7hr">
            Zugang anfordern
          </a>
          
          <a href="/use-cases/product-safety-recalls/" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-10 py-4 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 text-white font-semibold rounded-xl hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-300" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:1gb7hq">
            Sicherheit &amp; Rückrufe
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 2. The Landscape -->
  <section class="py-32 bg-white relative overflow-hidden" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:cloe6r">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:6g627t">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:6g627s">
        <div class="relative opacity-0 -translate-x-12 transition-all duration-1000" data-reveal="fade-right" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:6g627r">
          <div class="absolute -top-12 -left-12 w-24 h-24 bg-blue-100/50 rounded-full blur-2xl" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:accent-3"></div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 leading-[1.15] relative" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:e4yr2w">
            In der Medizin- und Lebensmittelbranche wird Vertrauen durch <span class="italic font-serif text-blue-600" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:9eb0t4">Klarheit</span> gewonnen.
          </h2>
          <div class="mt-12 space-y-8" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:landscape-text">
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:landscape-p1">
              TieBack
              hilft Marken dabei, Produktinformationen aktuell zu halten, Sicherheitshinweise präzise zu kommunizieren und Reibungsverluste für Verbraucher und Support-Teams zu reduzieren.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-medium text-slate-900" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:landscape-p2">
              TieBack
              gibt Produkten eine lebendige digitale Identität, sodass Sicherheitsstatus, Produktinformationen und Verbraucherhinweise stets aktuell bleiben – ohne dass man sich auf Verpackungsaktualisierungen oder umfangreiche manuelle Kommunikationsmaßnahmen verlassen muss.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative group opacity-0 translate-x-12 transition-all duration-1000" data-reveal="fade-left" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:6g627q">
           <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-600 rounded-[2.5rem] rotate-2 scale-95 opacity-10 group-hover:rotate-1 transition-transform duration-500" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:img-accent"></div>
           <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1651525670033-279c26cc2347?auto=format&w=1200&q=80"
            srcset="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1651525670033-279c26cc2347?auto=format&w=320&q=80 320w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1651525670033-279c26cc2347?auto=format&w=480&q=80 480w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1651525670033-279c26cc2347?auto=format&w=640&q=80 640w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1651525670033-279c26cc2347?auto=format&w=768&q=80 768w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1651525670033-279c26cc2347?auto=format&w=1024&q=80 1024w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1651525670033-279c26cc2347?auto=format&w=1280&q=80 1280w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1651525670033-279c26cc2347?auto=format&w=1920&q=80 1920w"
            sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 50vw"
            alt="Food manufacturing and packaging" class="relative z-10 w-full aspect-[4/3] object-cover rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-2xl" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:landscape-img" crossorigin="anonymous" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 3. Core Pillars (Modern Grid) -->
  <section class="py-32 bg-slate-50" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:cloe6s">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:6g627o">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-20" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:pillar-header">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:pillar-title">Warum „TieBack“</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:pillar-desc">Eine strukturierte Identitätsschicht, damit Marken Informationen veröffentlichen, diese marktbezogen lokalisieren und den Sicherheitsstatus aktualisieren können, ohne auf umfangreiche, manuelle Rückrufprozesse angewiesen zu sein.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:6g627m">
        
        <!-- Pillar 1: Safety communication -->
        <div class="group bg-white p-10 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 hover:border-blue-200 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-blue-500/5 transition-all duration-500 flex flex-col h-full opacity-0 translate-y-12 data-reveal-delay-100" data-reveal="fade-up" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:pillar-1">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:bg-blue-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300 relative" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:pillar-icon-1">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/>
              <line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/>
              <line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:stdoaj">Präzise Sicherheitskommunikation</h3>
          
          <div class="space-y-6 flex-grow" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:pillar-content-1">
            <div data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:tieback-part-1">
              <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest block mb-2" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:lbl-1">TieBack</span>
              <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:txt-1">Zeitgebundene Sicherheitshinweise und Rückrufmeldungen, die auf der richtigen Detailebene – Produkt, Variante oder Chargenstrategie – angewendet werden können und bei Bedarf übersichtlich oben im Passport angezeigt werden.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pt-6 border-t border-slate-100 mt-auto" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:gap-part-1">
              <span class="text-slate-600 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest block mb-2" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:lbl-gap-1">Die Lücke</span>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:txt-gap-1">Rückrufe stützen sich oft auf pauschale Chargenmitteilungen per E-Mail oder Pressemitteilungen. Verbraucher übersehen diese, die Kommunikation wird inkonsistent, und Maßnahmen lassen sich am Einsatzort schwerer steuern.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Pillar 2: Transparency -->
